com.ibm.ecm.api.coresdk.model

Interface IBMECMContentClass

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IBMECMBaseObject>, IBMECMBaseObject, Serializable

    public interface IBMECMContentClass
extends IBMECMBaseObject
    Represents a class definition or a metadata of a class. A content class provides a template of how an item can be constructed. The list of retrieveContentClassAttributeDefinitions(IBMECMCompletionHandler) matches the list of attributes and properties of an item constructed from this class.
